'''Common Monetary Area''' (CMA) e hlomaganya [[Afrika Borwa]], [[Lesotho]] le [[Eswatini]] go [[monetary union|mašeleng a lekgotla]]. CMA e thekgwa ke [[Southern African Customs Union]] (SACU). 

[[Namibia]] e bile leloko morago ga boipušô, e fela ya e kgogela morago ka 1993. Dollar ya Namibia, [[lilangeni]] ya [[Eswatini]] le [[loti]] ya [[Lesotho]] di lekana le [[South African Rand|ranta]] ya [[Afrika Borwa]]. Ranta ea dumelaga ebile ea dinageng tse.

Go maloko a [[Southern African Customs Union|SACU]] [[Botswana]] ke yona fela esego leloko la CMA.

